                                                <TextBlock FontFamily="Consolas" FontSize="12" Foreground="#90CBF9" TextWrapping="Wrap">dotnet publish ReaperPluginManager.csproj -c Release -r win-x64 --self-contained true /p:PublishSingleFile=true -o ./publish</TextBlock>
